flowchart TD
    Client([External Client])
    APIM[Apigee / APIM\nQuota Enforcement]
    ATM[Azure Traffic Manager\nDNS Load Balancing]
    front12[front12-deployment\nHTTP Frontend]
    Pulsar[(Apache Pulsar\nMessage Broker)]
    backend12[backend12-deployment\nBatch Processor]
    Blob[(Azure Blob Storage\nResult Store)]
    Underlying[Underlying Services\nRouting API / Search API / ...]

    Client -->|HTTPS| APIM
    APIM -->|quota-checked request| ATM
    ATM -->|region-routed request| front12
    front12 -->|enqueue job| Pulsar
    front12 -->|202 Accepted| Client
    Pulsar -->|dequeue job| backend12
    backend12 -->|HTTP + client API key| Underlying
    backend12 -->|store result| Blob
    Client -->|poll result| front12
    front12 -->|read result| Blob

    subgraph batch-service2-1.2 [Batch and Matrix 1.2 - batch-service2-1.2]
        front12
        backend12
    end

    subgraph infra [Shared Infrastructure - batch-service2-infra]
        Pulsar
        Blob
        ATM
        APIM
    end

    subgraph matrixv2 [Matrix Routing v2 - batch-service2]
        frontV2[front-deployment\nHTTP Frontend - Matrix v2]
        backendV2[backend-deployment\nBatch Processor - Matrix v2]
    end

    ATM -->|Matrix v2 traffic| frontV2
    frontV2 -->|enqueue| Pulsar
    Pulsar -->|dequeue| backendV2
    backendV2 -->|HTTP + client API key| Underlying
    backendV2 -->|store result| Blob
